{"tid":1373380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔裝telegram都可以睇到 telegram channel 既方法","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T14:03:11.000Z","uid":251295,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e721ec74c70d010450291b2fd42a3ff07bdabdf3","tid":1373380,"uid":251295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:19:53.000Z","msg":"有部份人可能因為無太空咭或者未用過telegram而無辦法睇到telegram channel 既資訊。<br />\n以下方法希望幫到大家（由其係文宣方面可以更容易流傳比所有人睇）<br />\n<br />\n方法好簡單，只要係原本既telegram link中間加/s/<br />\n以民陣個telegram channel為例<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3oTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=be19ef00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront</a><br />\n<br />\n只要改成<a href=\"https://t.me/s/CivilHumanRightsFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fs%2FCivilHumanRightsFront&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3oTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=5dc65491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/s/CivilHumanRightsFront</a><br />\n就可以直接用browser睇到channel內容。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家廣傳！"},{"pid":"a2b57ae4748b70ae186d8bb317e84ceb5311cc1d","tid":1373380,"uid":166860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:54:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"954103eeee5deae5f6c5430100485b635887c017","tid":1373380,"uid":119454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:10:33.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"13520664f9151211dc5cfd2cb3fdc275f95894c5","tid":1373380,"uid":14543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:03:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}